item.title: What?
item.description: Kayne asks great questions (kwestions) in his lyrics. How to use Kwestions for introspection Make a hot drink of your choice. How to Play Kwestions? Get together with friends Take it in turns to ask a Kwestion Everyone else writes or draws their response Fold up your Kwestion answer and put it in the middle The Kwestion asker reads and shows each in turn and chooses their favourite 6.
